        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 px-md-5 mx-md-5">
            <p class="text-black our-font mb-md-4 pe-2 px-md-0 mx-md-0">
                Create your charity's visibility, engagement and donations with
                our expert Social Media Optimization Services both Social Media
                Marketing (SMM) and Social Media Optimization (SMO), designed to
                attract more donors across all the digital platforms.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Section one End -->

    <!-- Image section Start Here -->
    <div class="container mb-5">
        <img
            src="/assets/img/service/website-development2.png"
            alt="Website Development"
            class="img-fluid"
        />
    </div>
    <!-- Image section End Here -->

    <!-- Section Two Start -->
    <div class="section-two container d-md-flex align-items-center col-12 my-5">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-7 pe-2 me-2 pe-md-5 me-md-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-black display-6">
                Increase Your Donations With Social Media Marketing
            </h2>
            <p class="text-black mb-md-4 pe-2 px-md-0 mx-md-0 our-font">
                Boost your nonprofit's fundraising efforts with Techno Serve's
                expert social media marketing services. By leveraging targeted
                strategies, we help you reach a broader audience, engage
                potential donors, and inspire action. <br /><br />
                Our approach focuses on creating compelling content, optimizing ad
                campaigns, and utilizing data-driven insights to maximize your impact
                across platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter. <br
                /><br />
