                efforts, Techno Serve ensures your message resonates with the right
                people, turning online interactions into meaningful donations that
                support your cause. Elevate your donations today with our specialized
                social media marketing solutions.
            </p>
            <div class="d-md-flex mb-4 text-start">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-7 px-md-0 px-2">
