                            What is the difference between Social Media
                            Marketing (SMM) and Social Media Optimization (SMO)?
                        </button>
                    </h3>
                    <div
                        id="collapseOne"
                        class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                        aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
                    >
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p class="our-font">
                                SMM focuses on creating and running ad campaigns
                                to engage with potential donors, while SMO
                                involves optimizing your social media profiles
                                and content to increase visibility and organic
                                reach.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button
                            class="accordion-button collapsed"
