                            How can Techno Serve’s Social Media Optimization
                            Services help increase donations for my charity?
                        </button>
                    </h3>
                    <div
                        id="collapseTwo"
                        class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                        aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
                    >
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p class="our-font">
                                Our services enhance your charity’s visibility,
                                engage potential donors, and optimize content
                                across platforms, leading to higher donations by
                                connecting with the right audience.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button
                            class="accordion-button collapsed"
                            type="button"
                            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseThree"
                        >
                            Which social media platforms does Techno Serve
                            specialize in for charity campaigns?
                        </button>
                    </h3>
                    <div
                        id="collapseThree"
                        class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                        aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
                    >
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p class="our-font">
                                We specialize in Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn,
                                Twitter, YouTube, and TikTok, crafting
                                strategies tailored to each platform's unique
                                audience to maximize your charity's impact.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button
                            class="accordion-button collapsed"
                            type="button"
                            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFour"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseFour"
                        >
                            How does Techno Serve ensure that my charity's
                            message resonates with potential donors?
                        </button>
                    </h3>
                    <div
                        id="collapseFour"
                        class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                        aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
                    >
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p class="our-font">
                                We use data-driven insights to create compelling
                                content and targeted ad campaigns, ensuring your
                                message reaches and engages the right people,
                                turning online interactions into meaningful
                                donations.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item mb-5">
                    <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                        <button
                            class="accordion-button collapsed"
                            type="button"
                            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFive"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="collapseFive"
                        >
                            Can you provide examples of successful social media
                            campaigns you’ve managed for other charities?
                        </button>
                    </h3>
                    <div
                        id="collapseFive"
                        class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                        aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
                    >
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p class="our-font">
                                Yes, we have a portfolio of successful projects
                                that showcase our expertise in driving
                                engagement and donations through well-executed
                                social media strategies. Let our results speak
                                for themselves.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
